# Terraform Lab 001 - Create AWS Key Pair

## Objective
Create an AWS EC2 Key Pair named `datacenter-kp` using Terraform.

## Resources
- tls_private_key
- aws_key_pair
- local_file

## Commands

```bash
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply
```

## Skills Learned
- Terraform resources
- AWS Provider
- TLS Provider
- Local Provider
- Creating EC2 Key Pairs
